<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ز م ر ذ:</span> <span class="c2">(الزُّمُرُّذُ)</span> بِضَمِّ الرَّاءِ وَتَشْدِيدِهَا الزَّبَرْجَدُ الْمَعْرُوفُ وَهُوَ مُعَرَّبٌ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>